@fairlysleepy CW is a Tv channel for the young, basically. Shaw and Wilde are my British (Irish) go to as social satire goes on stage, there is a lot of that in whodunnits too. 

While I find MY classics eloquent and hilarious, you watch sitcoms..At times, pure copy/paste from Brits. Like in a South Park special though : make them suck ! 

The Residence is a gem people spit on because it's "woke" or slow for a whodunnit. It's a comedy !
